{"questionId":"11847","questionHtml":"<p>Find the steady state probability vector for this Markov chain.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {0.4}&amp;{0.3} \\\\   {0.6}&amp;{0.7}  \\end{array}} \\right)\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   {1 - p}  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   {1 - p}  \\end{array}} \\right) \\Rightarrow 0.4p + 0.3\\left( {1 - p} \\right) = p \\Rightarrow p = \\frac{1}{3}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0.4</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0.3</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0.6</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0.7</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>p</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>p</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mn>0.4</mn>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>0.3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>p</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>So&nbsp;vector is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\tfrac{1}{3}} \\\\   {\\tfrac{2}{3}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>[or by investigating high powers of the transition matrix]</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3&nbsp;marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11847","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.17c","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the steady state probability vector for this Markov chain.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.19—Transition matrices – Markov chains"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}